title: NFL Draft Risers and Fallers with R.J. White (Football 4/3)
description:
Will Brinson breaks down the latest news and notes from around the NFL, including the AAF folding, Russell Wilson's contract demands and then he's joined by R.J. White to talk about the biggest risers and fallers in the NFL Draft as well as some sneaky team needs from around the league.
